        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIn last sonar fix patch, sonar plugin version was removed to inherit all settings from oparent pom.xml and only overrode those sonar properties that seemed necessary.\n\nThough first https://jenkins.onap.org/view/appc/job/appc-master-release-version-java-daily/172/ job succeeded, subsequent jobs have failed citing sonar plugin error:\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/view/appc/job/appc-master-release-version-java-daily/\n\nSome research on this suggests the errors derive from using version 3.3 of sonar plugin.",
